Privacy Policy

Adhkar we built this app as a Free app. This SERVICE is provided by Ay_attia at no cost and is intended for use as is.

Information Collection and Use

This app does not collect any personal information from the user.

The app may request access to:

Location (GPS): to calculate prayer times and find Qibla direction.

Notifications: to remind you of prayer times and daily Adhkar.


These permissions are only used for the core functionality of the app and are never stored, shared, or sold to third parties.

Third Party Services 

The app may use third-party services (such as Google AdMob) to display ads. These third-party services may collect information used to identify you (such as device information, approximate location, or advertising ID).

Link to privacy policy of third-party providers used by the app:

